examples.en: He is adamant in his refusal to change his mind.
She begged me to change my mind, but I remained adamant.
We've tried to talk him into coming with us, but he's adamant about staying here.
Britain is adamantly opposed to the new directive.
Michael Jackson is adamant that he will not tour this year.
She remained adamant about getting the actor's autograph even after he had disappeared backstage.
